data.title: WATCH: Sigourney Weaver Stars In This Powerful Short Movie About Aliens Occupying Earth
data.meta_description: 'District 9' and 'Elysium' director Neill Blomkamp's new short, 'Rakka', sees a post-apocalyptic Earth occupied by aliens.
